						<summary>

						<p>On the base of a <hi rend="italic">dhvajastaṁbha</hi> in a betel-garden called ‘Kambadagaḍḍa-maḍi’.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1527, Pramādicha, Jyēshṭha, ba. 30.</p>						

						<p>Records the remission of the <hi rend="italic">bhikshāvṛitti</hi> taxes due by the barbers in the Guṇḍugaṇḍi-<hi rend="italic">sthala</hi> by Nalagoṇḍamanāyani Bāli-Nāyaka on the representation of the barber Siṅgōju.</p>						

						</summary>
