<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī jayābhyu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>daya śālivāhana śaka 
<lb n="3"/>varṣaṁbulu 1005 
<lb n="4"/>27 Agunēṭi pramā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dica saṁvatsara jyē 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṣṭa ba 30 lu śrīmaṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nmahānāyaṁkācā 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ryulayina nalagoṁḍama 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nāyani bālināyanigā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ru tama nāyaṁkarāniki 
<lb n="11"/>celle guṁḍugaṁḍastalamaṁ 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>du kaligina bhikṣāvati kā 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nike maṁgalasiṁgoju mā 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ru manivigā telapagānu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15"/>sūrya caṁdralu 
<lb n="16"/>galaṁttakālamu 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>nnubhikṣāvṛti 
<lb n="18"/>maṁggaḷapaṁnnu ma 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>nyaṁgānu maṁ 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>nnistimi yiṁduku 
<lb n="21"/>yavaru tappinānu kāsi 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>lō brāhmaṇani caṁppina pā 
<lb n="23" break="no"/>pānabōduru 
</p>

